{% extends "base.jinja" %}

{% block title %}Community{% endblock title %}

{% block header %}
<h1>The Avali Community</h1>
{% endblock header %}

{% block content %}
<div class="content">
    <p>
        The avali community is spread wide, among many different platforms, including a subreddit,
        a couple discord servers, VRChat meetups, Resonite and even a Minecraft server!
    </p>
    <p>
        This section of the website aims to act as a hub, allowing all avali to find their bretheren,
        no matter where they are.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <h2>Organised Groups</h2>
    <div class="dock">
        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Avali Army</h3>
            <p>Avali-focused Discord server, home of the Da'Vali model, the Avalicraft Minecraft server and VRChat
                meetups!</p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://discord.gg/avali">Join them! (Discord)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Lost Community</h3>
            <p>General Avali Discord server, focused around the Lost Avali stickers! Also has a VRchat group.</p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://discord.gg/bV6r6eUVSp">Join them! (Discord)</a>
                </div>
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://discord.gg/bV6r6eUVSp">Join them! (VRChat)</a>
                </div>
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://telegram.me/addstickers/lostavali">Grab the telegram sticker pack (1)</a>
                </div>
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://telegram.me/addstickers/loststickervol2">Grab the telegram sticker pack (2)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Space Bird Federation</h3>
            <p>Semi-roleplay Discord server, also holds VRChat meetups and Wiggle Wednesdays</p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://discord.gg/bV6r6eUVSp">Join them! (Discord)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pod">
            <h3>r/avali</h3>
            <p>The avali subreddit! Lots of art is posted here.</p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://reddit.com/r/avali">Join them! (Reddit)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pod">
            <h3>The Avali wiki!</h3>
            <p>Yep, we have a fandom wiki.</p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://avali.fandom.com/wiki/The_Official_Avali_Wiki">Join them! (Fandom)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <h2>Other places to find fellow avali</h2>
    <div class="dock">
        <div class="pod">
            <h3>VRChat</h3>
            <p>VRChat has a significant avali population, try looking in furry instances!</p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://hello.vrchat.com/">Join them! (Website)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Resonite</h3>
            <p>
                Resonite also has a significant avali population! I would say to look in
                furry instances, but this is Resonite, every instance is a furry instance!
            </p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://hello.vrchat.com/">Join them! (Website)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

{% endblock content %}